For me this is the best Iteration of this profile and even puts the Dinner Lady original in the shadows. &#xD;
Smooth, well layered liquid, awesome lemon taste that perfectly complements the cake base. &#xD;
&#xD;
The last part really is what impresses me because most lemon bakery liquids cant manage to combine the mostly sharp fruity lemon flavors into a full bodied bakery. &#xD;
Thanks for this outstanding recipe Daren
